Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   ATP
Formula: ADP + Pi → ATP
Note:    Universal energy currency of all living cells

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   2nd Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔS ≥ 0
Note:    Entropy always increases in isolated systems

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   1st Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔU = Q - W
Note:    Energy conservation in thermodynamic systems

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   E = mc²
Formula: E = mc²
Note:    Mass-energy equivalence; foundation of nuclear physics

